&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Join Our Growing Accounting Team!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mid-Atlantic Truck &amp;amp; Equipment is growing&lt;/strong&gt;, and we’re looking for a detail-oriented &lt;strong&gt;Accounts Payable Coordinator&lt;/strong&gt; to join our corporate team in Easton, MD. In this role, you’ll be responsible for supporting the day-to-day accounts payable functions and helping ensure accurate, timely processing of vendor invoices and payments across the organization.&lt;/p&gt;
