&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;We’re looking for an experienced&lt;strong&gt; Diesel Field Service Technician&lt;/strong&gt; to support customers throughout &lt;strong&gt;Henrico County, VA.&lt;/strong&gt; This is a great opportunity for a high-level technician who takes pride in their work, enjoys solving problems independently, and wants to be part of a strong team that respects skill, experience, and hard work.&lt;/p&gt;
